## To forcely reload image of a deployment
  `kubectl rollout restart deployment platforms-deployment`
  `kubectl rollout restart deployment commands-deployment`

## To get the current deployments
  `kubectl get deployments`

## To get the current deployed pods
  `kubectl get pods`

## To get the active services
  `kubectl get services`

## To get storageclass
  `kubectl get storageclasses`

## To get persistent volume claims
  `kubectl get persistentvolumeclaims`
  or
  `kubectl get pvc`

## To create secret that will be used for MSSQL database
  `kubectl create secret generic mssql --from-literal=SA_PASSWORD="<password>"`
